      "body" : "This looks to be the first mention of \"change\" period.  A rational user will think it relates to change returned by recipient for amount paid over some agreed-on price, which further confuses, since no such prices are known by bitcoin-qt.\r\n\r\nThe question is what should the message say, given the abstractions user is working with?  That is a tough one.\r\n",
